  "title": "Product Application Specialist - Furniture| AutoCAD| Project| MNC",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights</strong></p><ul><li><p>5 Working Days, Office Hours</p></li><li><p>Competitive remuneration package</p></li><li><p>Great Career Progression<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist with layout planning for floor markings and coordinate execution with the project team</p></li><li><p>Responsible for preparing drawings, presentations (PPT), and sharing materials with the sales team, clients, architects, and designers.</p></li><li><p>Liaises directly with customers, architects, and designers on drawings, specifications, and quotations.</p></li><li><p>Handles drawings and costings for projects.</p></li><li><p>Manages multiple clients and projects concurrently.</p></li><li><p>Work with the operations team to track order processing and follow up on status</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong written and verbal communication skills</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with project matrices, project specifications, CAD tools, order management, and quotation systems</p></li><li><p>Proficient in AutoCAD, SketchUp, Excel, MS Office, Adobe Acrobat, and other relevant software tools<br /></p></li></ul><p>To Apply, kindly click on the <strong>\"APPLY NOW\"</strong> button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><strong>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Yuphine Lee | R22108749</strong></p>",
